    <title type="html"><![CDATA[再谈自动生成ISO文件的客制化问题]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.xeonxu.info/blog/2013/05/13/zai-tan-zi-dong-sheng-cheng-isowen-jian-de-ke-zhi-hua-wen-ti/"/>
    <updated>2013-05-13T22:37:00+08:00</updated>
